* Connection
- logged in user has different conn object to local for dderl private use
- have_permission (manage_connection) if false
-   [have_permission ({ConnId, use}) -> true/false]
- have_permission ({ConnId, modify}) -> true (replace) / false (add new) -- when user tries to save a connection
- 'Connection Name' drop down -> user.conn_name (ex - "system.new conn" / "stefan.my conn")
- no 'Save' button
- Connection Save/Modified only on successful connect
- 'Login' -> 'Login / Save'

